{"tid":905471,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[Finance巴打入] Pecking Order Theory","createTime":"2018-11-17T06:57:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T06:57:33.000Z","uid":61797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7e1d58667df7ced9ee5c9147396c0fcc13cb3055","tid":905471,"uid":61797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T06:57:33.000Z","msg":"跟據Pecking order theory<br />\n一間公司首先會用retained earnings (R/E)<br />\n其次用borrowing (bank borrowing or bond)<br />\n最後先issue share capital<br />\n<br />\n假設1間公司買資產(Dr. PPE / Cr. Bank)都唔會郁到R/E舊數<br />\n睇財務報表只會見到今年既R/E係上年R/E+profit(loss)-dividend pay<br />\n咁睇一間公司既年報點先睇得出間公司優先選擇用R/E?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}